Exercise 16.51: Determine what sizeof...(Args) and
sizeof...(rest) return for each call to foo in this section.

Answer:
foo(i, s, 42, d); --> sizeof...(Args)  will return 2, sizeof...(rest) will return 3
foo(s, 42, "hi"); --> sizeof...(Args)  will return 2, sizeof...(rest) will return 2
foo(d, s); --> sizeof...(Args)  will return 2, sizeof...(rest) will return 1
foo("hi"); --> sizeof...(Args)  will return 2, sizeof...(rest) will return 0